descriptionHtml:
I have no experience with modding, and not a lot of time to try to make it myself. I just need someone who is skilled in it to help me with a small change to the game. I want the default male's voice for Khajit when casting Fire Breath to be changed to this: http://vocaroo.com/i/s0fqQMhPyEsL
And that's it! I would be very happy if someone could do this for me. Important for my modded character :) Make it loud, but not too loud. A bit louder than you can hear in the link here, but not too loud. Try to make it as loud as the default voice. I have a mod that lets me shout very frequently in exchange for Dragon Souls, so I don't want my ears to bleed just yet. I'd really appreciate it!
